<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_179" id="88r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_179_r2l15">Der Stat Ypphouen / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_179_r2l16">Lieben frewnde / Als Jꝛ vns <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habent von hanſen Sweinleins </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_179_r2l17">vnd Götʒen Kügeleins <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> wegen / daʒ haben vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_179_r2l18">vnd haben darümb / Peter voglern vnſern Burger beſant vnd cʒurede geſatʒt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_179_r2l19">der hat vns <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / es hab / Appell Todrer ſelig ein redlich geſcheft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_179_r2l20">getan / vnd voꝛmünde darüber geſetʒt / nach <expan>vnſer<ex>r</ex></expan> Stat gevvonheit / darbeÿ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_179_r2l21">es billich bleibe / heten aber darüber / die <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>mitburge<ex>r</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_179_r2l23">vnſern icht cʒu <expan>ſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> wöllen vvir 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_179_line_1575883518727_796">
<del rend="strikethrough">Jn </del></ab></add> <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>
<del rend="strikethrough"><ab facs="#facs_179_r2l22"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheinpo<ex>ten</ex></expan> </ab></del></add> <expan>vnuercʒoge<ex>n</ex>s</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_179_r2l25">
<add><ab facs="#facs_179_r1l1">
<del rend="strikethrough">mit <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> ge </del></ab><ab facs="#facs_179_r1l2">
<del rend="strikethrough">walt </del></ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> cʒogens </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_179_r2l24">Jn oder Jren <expan>ſcheinbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>Jre<ex>m</ex></expan> vollen gewalt vnuertʒogens </ab></add> ſlewnigs rechten <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hellffen vvenn wir des ermant vverden / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_179_r2l26">So der <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> vnſer Burger anheim iſt / vnd getrawen ew wol Jꝛ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_179_r2l27">weiſt die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> daran / daʒ ſie ſich daran benugen laſʒen <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_179" id="88r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat Ypphoven </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieben frewnde, als ir uns <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habent von
                        Hansen Sweinleins und Göczen Kügeleins, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wegen, daz haben wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und haben darümb Peter
                        Voglern, unsern burger, besant und czurede gesaczt; der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, es hab Appell Todrer selig ein
                        redlich gescheft getan und vormünde darüber geseczt nach
                                <expan>unser<ex>r</ex></expan> stat gewonheit, darbey es billich
                        bleibe; heten aber darüber die <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        ewr <expan>mitburge<ex>r</ex></expan>, czu <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        unsern icht czu <expan>spreche<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> wöllen wir <add>in oder iren
                                    <expan>scheinbote<ex>n</ex></expan> mit
                                <expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan> vollen gewalt unverczogens</add>
                        slewnigs rechten <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hellffen, wenn wir des ermant
                        werden, so der <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> unser burger anheim
                        ist; und getrawen ew wol, ir weist die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> daran,
                        daz sie sich daran benugen laszen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
